 >> ASM_REWRITE_TAC []
 >> `(!x. x IN s ==> f' x IN IMAGE f' s)` by METIS_TAC [IN_IMAGE]
 >> `(!x y. x IN s /\ y IN s ==> (f' x = f' y) ==> (x = y))` by METIS_TAC [IN_INSERT]
